#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_heads/init.lua:254
msgid "Zombie Head"
msgstr "Cabeza de zombie"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_heads/init.lua:255
msgid ""
"A zombie head is a small decorative block which resembles the head of a "
"zombie. It can also be worn as a helmet, which reduces the detection range "
"of zombies by 50%."
msgstr ""
"Una cabeza de zombie es un pequeño bloque decorativo. También se puede usar "
"como casco, lo que reduce el rango de detección de zombies en un 50%."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_heads/init.lua:264
msgid "Creeper Head"
msgstr "Cabeza de creeper"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_heads/init.lua:265
msgid ""
"A creeper head is a small decorative block which resembles the head of a "
"creeper. It can also be worn as a helmet, which reduces the detection range "
"of creepers by 50%."
msgstr ""
"La cabeza de un creeper es un pequeño bloque decorativo. También se puede "
"usar como casco, lo que reduce el rango de detección de los creepers en un "
"50%."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_heads/init.lua:275
msgid "Human Head"
msgstr "Cabeza humana"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_heads/init.lua:276
msgid ""
"A human head is a small decorative block which resembles the head of a human "
"(i.e. a player character). It can also be worn as a helmet for fun, but does "
"not offer any protection."
msgstr ""
"Una cabeza humana es un pequeño bloque decorativo que se asemeja a la cabeza "
"de un humano (es decir, un personaje jugador). También se puede usar como "
"casco por diversión, pero no ofrece ninguna protección."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_heads/init.lua:283
msgid "Skeleton Skull"
msgstr "Calavera de esqueleto"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_heads/init.lua:284
msgid ""
"A skeleton skull is a small decorative block which resembles the skull of a "
"skeleton. It can also be worn as a helmet, which reduces the detection range "
"of skeletons by 50%."
msgstr ""
"Una calavera es un pequeño bloque decorativo que se asemeja a la cabeza de "
"un esqueleto. También se puede usar como casco, lo que reduce el rango de "
"detección de esqueletos en un 50%."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_heads/init.lua:293
msgid "Wither Skeleton Skull"
msgstr "Calavera de esqueleto del Wither"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_heads/init.lua:294
msgid ""
"A wither skeleton skull is a small decorative block which resembles the "
"skull of a wither skeleton. It can also be worn as a helmet for fun, but "
"does not offer any protection."
msgstr ""
"Una cabeza de esqueleto marchito es un pequeño bloque decorativo que se "
"asemeja al cráneo de un esqueleto marchito. También se puede usar como casco "
"por diversión, pero no ofrece ninguna protección."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_heads/init.lua:303
msgid "Piglin Head"
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_heads/init.lua:304
msgid ""
"A piglin head is a small decorative block which resembles the head of a "
"piglin. It can also be worn as a helmet, which reduces the detection range "
"of piglins by 50%."
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_heads/init.lua:326
msgid "Dragon Head"
msgstr "Cabeza de Dragón"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_heads/init.lua:327
msgid ""
"A dragon head is a decorative block which resembles the head of a dragon. It "
"can also be worn as a helmet."
msgstr ""
